<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 qiān zhǒng xīn, wàn zhǒng kǔ, hái shì méi yǒu tíng zhǐ jiǎo bù.
 shù shù suì yuè, nán yàn běi fēi, réng yào tóng xíng zài fēng yǔ zhī lù.
 zài zhè lù shàng yào xué huì tiān tiān yǎng wàng zhǔ. zài zhè lù shàng dōu yào yǒu tǎn dàng de xīn tú.
 yè jǐn tiān zì míng, gān xīn qù chī kǔ, yī qiè dōu biàn chéng zhù fú.</lyrics>
<title>qiān zhǒng xīn wàn zhǒng kǔ 迦南489</title>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
